        Selling With a Development Approval in Brisbane: Does It Add Value?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A DA can change who buys your property and what they pay. Understanding both effects before you list gives you a real advantage.
      </p>
